29\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Hockey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same position\", \"from\": 59, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2025 4 Nations Face-Off\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What you need to know: He has the pedigree.\", \"from\": 182, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pedigree\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not only was he supposed to be the GM for the Beijing team before the NHL withdrew, but the 53-year-old represented the United States in the Olympics three times as a player (1998 in Nagano, 2002 in Salt Lake City and 2006 in Torino), winning a silver medal in 2002.\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.727700005603325e-23, \"text\": \"GM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_manager\"}, {\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Guoan_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beijing team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Guoan_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Guoan_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 297, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.472470703682956e-28, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}, {\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.023010236298406e-26, \"text\": \"Unite