tional_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Advertisement Guerin\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"18 years\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 531}, {\"ngram\": \"two Stanley Cups\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"theNew Jersey Devilsin\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"andPittsburgh Penguinsin\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"a Penguins executive\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Hockey Hall\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"Fame\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is tied for the eighth-most goals (429) amongst U.S.-born players in NHL history.\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.472470703682956e-28, \"text\": \"NHL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Hockey_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the eighth-most goals\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 796}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S.-born players\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am just super excited for this opportunity,\\\" Guerin toldThe Athleticon Thursday.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this opportunity\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was 9 years old when the Miracle on Ice happened, and that was very impactful in my life and my love for hockey and my desire to represent my country.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1085, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Miracle\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"Ice\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"